        whyItMatters: 'Reading v.18 as automatic forgiveness removes the urgency that the entire chapter is designed to create. The scarlet-to-snow offer is precious precisely because it can be refused. Grace that requires no response is not grace but indifference. The courtroom demands a verdict from the defendant.',
