        whyItMatters: 'If the reader hears only judgment, they will either despair or dismiss the chapter as irrelevant. But if they hear the invitation within the judgment \u2014 the grieving parent who accuses in order to restore \u2014 they encounter a God who is more relentless in mercy than in wrath.',
